<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='fr'>
<style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700");

    a {
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    body {
        font-size: 14px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        height: 95vh;
        overflow: scroll;
        font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex: 1;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .delete {
        font-weight: bold;
        justify-self: end;
        font-size: 10px;
    }

    .link {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .btn {
        background-color: darkblue;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .4);
        box-sizing: unset;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .text {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex: 1;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Merci <%= name %>, vous êtes inscrit</h1>

    <div class="text">
        <p>Vous venez de créer un compte.</p>
        <p>Cliquer sur le lien suivant pour vérifier votre compte.</p>
        <p class="delete">Sans verification votre compte sera supprimer le <%= time %>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
        <a class="btn"
           href="<% if(isDev) %>
                    <%= 'http://localhost:5000' %>
                <% else %>
                    <%= 'https://www.amstramgram.ml' %>
                    /email-verification?token=<%= confirmation_link %>">
            Confirmer mon inscription
        </a>
        <a href="http://amstramgram.ml" class="link">amstramgram</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
